A teenage boy drowned on Wednesday evening in Yahud Dam outside wajir town. It took residents four hours to retrieve the body for lack of experienced divers and rescue equipment.The boy's mother said he told her he was going for prayers. I was worried due to his long absence until I was visited by a group of young boys who told me my son was trapped in Yahud dam , said the mother, adding that she then raised an alarm and started efforts to retrieve her son s body.